@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_hnzcmq(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.cos((v2 + 0.52 - v0 + 0.86)) * (wp.exp(tmp + 0.84) + (tmp + 0.27 * v0 + 0.99)))
    v1 = v2
    v0 = wp.exp(v1)
    v0 = v1
    v1 = (0.21 / wp.abs((v0 + 0.13 / v0 + 0.30)))
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.abs((v0 + 0.24 * v1 + 0.59)))
    tmp = ((0.36 - (v0 + 0.97 / v2 + 0.42)) * 0.58)
    v0 = (wp.cos(0.02) + (wp.abs(v2 + 0.91) / (v1 + 0.61 - tmp + 0.68)))
    data[tid] = v0
